Food Truck Face Off - Season 1, Episode 5




Charnow Park Chowdown

The judges have a tough choice deciding which two teams of food truck wannabes should fight it out in Miami, Fla. Host Jesse Palmer takes the teams through their paces over the two sell days, with manic driving and panic prep fails on day one and the struggles of facing increased competition on day two.




Original Air Date: 23-Oct-2014
